Feature: Display central image corresponding to thumbnail
  In order to enlarge a thumbnail image
  Casual Users should be able to select a thumbnail to
  have it enlarged.

  Scenario: First time viewing a slide deck
    Given there are some thumbnails in the slide deck
    When the users opens the slide deck
    Then the first slide in the slide deck should be enlarged

  Scenario: Casual User selects a thumbnail
    Given there are some thumbnails in the slide deck
    When the user selects a different thumbnail in the slide deck
    Then the enlarged image should change to match the thumbnail
